Name: httpmodules
Type: BITFIELD
Allowed-Values: admin caldav carddav convert cgi domainkey freebusy ischedule
 jmap prometheus rss tzdist webdav
Default-Value:
Last-Modified: 3.1.7

Space-separated list of HTTP modules that will be enabled in
:cyrusman:`httpd(8)`.  Running multiple httpd instances, each with a
different :imapdconf:`httpmodules` value, is supported.

Note that "domainkey" depends on "ischedule" being enabled, and that both
"freebusy" and "ischedule" depend on "caldav" being enabled.

The "convert" module is experimental and is not meant for production use.
